author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Sharing Economy International Enters Into Exclusivity Agreement With JoGeep
text:
Jan 29 (Reuters) - Sharing Economy International Inc :
* SHARING ECONOMY INTERNATIONAL ENTERS INTO EXCLUSIVITY AGREEMENT WITH JOGEEP REGARDING POTENTIAL ACQUISITION TO EXPAND TRAVEL RENTAL SERVICES WITH BLOCKCHAIN AND A.I. PLATFORM
* SHARING ECONOMY INTERNATIONAL - UNIT ENTERED INTO DEAL WITH SHAREHOLDERS OF JOGEEP REGARDING POTENTIAL DEAL BY EC RENTAL OF NOT LESS THAN 51 PCT OF JOGEEP Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
